No. 10-732. Shirley Edwards, Petitioner v. A.H. Cornell and Son, Inc., dba AH Cornells, et al. 562 U.S. 1280, 131 S. Ct. 1604,

179 L. Ed. 2d 517,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2092. March 7, 2011.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 610 F.3d 217.
